<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Us</title>
    <style>
        body, html {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            height: 100%;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        }
        .container {
            display: flex;
            height: 100%;
            background-color: #f0f0f0;
            padding: 1rem;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        .sidebar {
            width: 4rem;
            background-color: #e0e0e0;
            border-radius: 1rem 0 0 1rem;
            padding: 0.5rem;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: space-between;
        }
        .sidebar-button {
            width: 2rem;
            height: 2rem;
            background-color: #c0c0c0;
            border-radius: 50%;
            margin: 0.5rem auto;
        }
        .main-content {
            flex: 1;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            margin-left: 1rem;
        }
        .header {
            height: 3rem;
            background-color: #e0e0e0;
            border-radius: 1rem 1rem 0 0;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 0 1rem;
        }
        .header-button {
            width: 1.5rem;
            height: 1.5rem;
            background-color: #c0c0c0;
            border-radius: 50%;
            margin-right: 1rem;
        }
        .header-title {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-right: auto;
        }
        .content {
            flex: 1;
            background-color: #e0e0e0;
            border-radius: 1rem;
            padding: 1rem;
            overflow-y: auto;
        }
        .about-section {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 0.5rem;
            padding: 1rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }
        .about-section h2 {
            margin-top: 0;
            color: #333;
        }
        .about-section p {
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #666;
        }
        .team-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(150px, 1fr));
            gap: 1rem;
            margin-top: 1rem;
        }
        .team-member {
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
            border-radius: 0.5rem;
            padding: 0.5rem;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .team-member-image {
            width: 100px;
            height: 100px;
            background-color: #c0c0c0;
            border-radius: 50%;
            margin: 0 auto 0.5rem;
        }
        .team-member-name {
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
        }
        .team-member-role {
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            color: #666;
        }
        .bottom-section {
            height: 4rem;
            background-color: #e0e0e0;
            border-radius: 1rem;
            margin-top: 1rem;
            padding: 1rem;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }
        .social-links {
            display: flex;
            gap: 1rem;
        }
        .social-icon {
            width: 2rem;
            height: 2rem;
            background-color: #c0c0c0;
            border-radius: 50%;
        }
        .contact-button {
            padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
            background-color: #4CAF50;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 0.25rem;
            cursor: pointer;
        }
        .right-sidebar {
            width: 12rem;
            margin-left: 1rem;
        }
        .right-top, .right-bottom {
            background-color: #e0e0e0;
            border-radius: 1rem;
            padding: 1rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }
        .right-top {
            height: 10rem;
        }
        .right-bottom {
            height: calc(100% - 12rem);
        }
        h3 {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            margin: 0 0 0.5rem 0;
        }
        .mission-statement {
            font-style: italic;
            color: #333;
            line-height: 1.4;
        }
        .timeline {
            list-style-type: none;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .timeline li {
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
            padding-left: 1rem;
            position: relative;
        }
        .timeline li::before {
            content: '';
            width: 0.5rem;
            height: 0.5rem;
            background-color: #4CAF50;
            border-radius: 50%;
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            top: 0.4rem;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('../partials/header.ejs') %>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="sidebar">
            <div>
                <div class="sidebar-button"></div>
                <div class="sidebar-button"></div>
                <div class="sidebar-button"></div>
                <div class="sidebar-button"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="sidebar-button"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="main-content">
            <div class="header">
                <div class="header-button"></div>
                <div class="header-button"></div>
                <div class="header-button"></div>
                <div class="header-title">About Us</div>
            </div>
            <div class="content">
                <div class="about-section">
                    <h2>Our Story</h2>
                    <p>Founded in 2010, our company has been at the forefront of innovation in the tech industry. We started with a simple idea: to make technology accessible to everyone. Over the years, we've grown from a small startup to a global leader, but our core mission remains the same.</p>
                    <p>We believe in the power of technology to transform lives and businesses. Our team of dedicated professionals works tirelessly to develop cutting-edge solutions that address real-world challenges.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="about-section">
                    <h2>Our Team</h2>
                    <p>Meet the passionate individuals who drive our success:</p>
                    <div class="team-grid">
                        <div class="team-member">
                            <div class="team-member-image"></div>
                            <div class="team-member-name">John Doe</div>
                            <div class="team-member-role">CEO</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="team-member">
                            <div class="team-member-image"></div>
                            <div class="team-member-name">Jane Smith</div>
                            <div class="team-member-role">CTO</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="team-member">
                            <div class="team-member-image"></div>
                            <div class="team-member-name">Mike Johnson</div>
                            <div class="team-member-role">Lead Developer</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="team-member">
                            <div class="team-member-image"></div>
                            <div class="team-member-name">Sarah Williams</div>
                            <div class="team-member-role">UX Designer</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="bottom-section">
                <div class="social-links">
                    <div class="social-icon"></div>
                    <div class="social-icon"></div>
                    <div class="social-icon"></div>
                </div>
                <button class="contact-button">Contact Us</button>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="right-sidebar">
            <div class="right-top">
                <h3>OUR MISSION</h3>
                <p class="mission-statement">"To empower individuals and businesses through innovative technology solutions, fostering growth and positive change in the world."</p>
            </div>
            <div class="right-bottom">
                <h3>COMPANY MILESTONES</h3>
                <ul class="timeline">
                    <li>2010: Company founded</li>
                    <li>2013: Launch of first product</li>
                    <li>2016: Expansion to international markets</li>
                    <li>2019: Reached 1 million users</li>
                    <li>2022: Named "Top Innovator" by Tech Magazine</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>